title: Palisades' Cooper Moyer is lehighvalleylive Boys Soccer Player of the Week
text:
Palisades' Cooper Moyer is the lehighvalleylive Boys Soccer Player of the Week. (lehighvalleylive.com file photo) By Kyle Craig | For lehighvalleylive.com on October 02, 2015 3:00 PM, updated October 02, 2015 4:07 PM 
BOYS SOCCER PLAYER OF THE WEEK Cooper Moyer (Courtesy photo) 
Cooper Moyer , Palisades 
The junior forward continues to climb up the areaâ€™s goal scoring charts and had his two most productive games of the season over the last week. 
Moyer tallied seven goals and four assists as the Pirates routed Catasauqua (8-1) and Pen Argyl (7-2). He has 21 goals through 11 games this fall after recording 22 goals during his sophomore campaign. 
Honorable mention : Sr. FWD Zachary Adams , Salisbury; Jr. MID Noah Bacon , Emmaus; Sr. FWD Gino Boscia , Pen Argyl; So. FWD Ryan Keenan , Northampton; sr. MID/FWD Tyler Madeira , Parkland; Jr. FWD Abe Meral , Liberty; Sr. MID Joe Nguyen , Central Catholic; Sr. MID Jack Painter , Moravian Academy; Sr. FWD Steven Riad , Freedom.
